race.description: Sublime Aluminium & Glass Somersby Sprint Hcp
race.comment: SUPER FREDS (9) doesn't win out of turn but gets the right set-up for this with the big drop in weight. Surged late for a narrow second over 1000m at Muswellbrook in a C2. Has a good record here and looks the value play. BREMEL (2) lightly raced mare with a good winning record. Up in class on resumption when racing in restricted room for a fading ninth over 1000m at Eagle Farm. Can race closer from the inside gate today and take catching. CANI CANCAN (4) hunted out from the wide barrier and the early effort told late when a dismal eleventh over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Gets no favours again today and can improve in this easier contest. MR TRACKSIDE (10) turned in a much better performance second-up and is good enough to test some of these.
